<div class="ga-shipping-page-wrapper" style="padding: 2rem 0; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-sans);">
  
  <!-- Editorial Page Header -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-header-editorial" style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto 6rem auto; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ga-border-color); padding-bottom: 4rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem;">
    <span class="ga-subtitle" style="color: var(--ga-gold-cream); font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; font-weight: 700;">SATISFACTION & QUALITY ASSURED</span>
    <h1 class="ga-title" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.4rem); font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--ga-forest-green);">Refund & Return Policy</h1>
    <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
      We stand behind the purity and heritage of our wood-fired A2 Bilona Ghee. Because we care about your experience, we offer a transparent quality guarantee.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Text-Based Policy Content -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-content-block" style="max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto 6rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    
    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">1. Food Safety & Return Nature</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Ghar Aangan A2 Ghee is a raw, artisanal food product simmered in small batches. To maintain strict health, safety, and hygiene standards, <strong>we do not accept physical returns or exchanges of opened, seal-broken, or consumed jars</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        However, your satisfaction is extremely important to us. If you experience a genuine quality issue or notice any packaging defects upon arrival, please contact our support team within <strong>7 days of delivery</strong>. We address concerns on a case-by-case basis and will offer replacements or store credits for verified issues.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">2. 100% Transit Guarantee (Damages)</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        To ensure zero plastic interaction with our hot-filled ghee, we store it in food-grade glass jars. While glass maintains peak freshness, it can occasionally crack during heavy shipping handlers. We offer a <strong>complete, hassle-free replacement guarantee for transit damages</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        If your glass jar arrives broken, leaking, or compromised, do not worry. Simply email us at <strong>support@gharaangan.com</strong> or message us on WhatsApp within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> with a clear photo or video showing the damaged bottle and package. We will process and ship a brand-new replacement jar at no extra cost.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.15s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">3. Order Cancellations</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        We strive to ship orders quickly to ensure fast delivery. You can cancel your order free of charge within <strong>12 hours</strong> of placing it, or before it has been dispatched from our facility, whichever occurs first.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        Once an order has been picked up by our logistics partner and a tracking ID has been generated, we are unable to cancel the shipment or recall the package, and standard shipping policies will apply.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">4. Refund Settlements & Timelines</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        Once a refund is approved by our customer support desk:
      </p>
      <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-sans); font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--ga-gold-cream);">✦</span>
          <strong>Prepaid Orders:</strong> The refund will be credited directly back to your original payment source (Credit/Debit Card, Netbanking, or UPI wallet). This transaction normally reflects within <strong>5 to 7 business days</strong> depending on your banking provider.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--ga-gold-cream);">✦</span>
          <strong>Cash on Delivery (COD) Orders:</strong> Because we do not store COD payment coordinates, refunds will be settled via direct bank transfer (NEFT) or UPI. Our support team will securely request your details to initiate the payout.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Section (Single Column Text Layout) -->
