    <div class="ga-faq-container">
      
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Can I get a refund if I do not like the taste or smoky aroma?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            Our A2 Ghee is prepared using traditional wood-fired Bilona churning. This authentic process infuses a rich, smoky aroma and a beautifully granular texture that differs from factory-produced ghee. Because taste and aroma are subjective preferences, we cannot offer refunds based on personal flavor choices. However, if you believe your jar has a quality issue, please contact us for a review.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Do I need to mail the broken glass jar back to you?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            No, for safety reasons, we strictly request that you do not package or ship back broken glass. Once our customer care team verifies the transit damage through a photo or video sent via WhatsApp or email, we will instruct you to safely dispose of the broken jar, and we will initiate the replacement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>How long does it take for a replacement order to reach me?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            Once a transit damage claim or order error is approved, we dispatch a fresh replacement jar from our inventory within 24 hours. The delivery will follow standard transit durations: 3 to 5 business days for Metros, and 5 to 7 business days for the rest of India.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="ga-faq-details">
        <summary class="ga-faq-summary">
          <span>Are shipping and COD convenience fees refundable?</span>
          <span class="ga-faq-icon">✦</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="ga-faq-content">
          <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
            Flat shipping fees (₹99 for orders below ₹1,499) and Cash on Delivery service fees (₹49) represent direct charges paid to our logistics providers for physical labor and are non-refundable, unless the order is cancelled prior to leaving our dispatch warehouse.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>

